	• First install ubuntu from ms store --> create user -- > riyonis-->boombaby69 [username & pass]
	New User
	• Type in add user --> sudo adduser nrupa --> put pass above -- it will ask new pass again and type in again 
	• Enter the new values and leave it same -- enter 4 times --- click yes -- now user has been added 
	Key generation
	• ssh-keygen --> enter --enter passphrase - enter until key generated 
	• sudo apt update(updates packages)--->enter pass
	• sudo apt install ansible -y --->ansible --version
	Create inventory file 
	•  vi inventory.ini --> type localhost ansible_connection=local--->press esc -- type :wq (enter)
	Executing inventory file
	•  ansible-inventory -i inventory.ini --list
	Checking ping for this
	•  ansible all -i inventory.ini -m ping
	Creating playbook
	•  nano basic_playbook.yml --- > copy paste the below --> and to save ctrl+o --> enter --> ctrl+x to exit 
	- name: Create a directory 
	  hosts: localhost tasks: 
	  name: Create the 'my_test_directory' 
	  ansible.builtin.file: 
	      path: /tmp/my_test_directory 
	      state: directory
	•  ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini basic_playbook.yml (playbook name given)
	Repeat step by making change in so it shows changes made 1
